title: Gelish - House of Gelish Collection - My Favorite Accessory #01439
description: 1. Sanitize, prep, and push back cuticles. Then wipe with Hand and Nail Harmony Cleanser using a lint-free wipe. Apply Hand & Nail Harmony PH Bond. 2. Apply Gelish Foundation Gel in a thin application and seal the edge of the nail. 3. Place hand in the LED light for 10 seconds or 1 minute in a UV light. 4. Lightly remove residue from the nail with a clean gel brush. 5. Apply Gelish color of choice in a thin application from cuticle to free edge. Be sure to seal the edges of the nail. 6. Place hand in LED light for 30 seconds or 2 minutes in a UV lamp. For darker coverage repeat steps 5 and 6. 7. Apply Gelish Top It Off Top Coat Sealer from cuticle to free edge using a light application. 8. Place hand in the LED light for 30 seconds or 2 minutes in a UV light. 9. Wipe off the Tacky layer with Hand & Nail Harmony Cleanser. Cure Time: - FOUNDATION GEL 10 SECONDS 1 MINUTE - STRUCTURE GEL 30 SECONDS 2 MINUTES - TOP IT OFF GEL 20-30 SECONDS 2 MINUTES - COLORS 20-30 SECONDS 2 MINUTES
